on (UCC) by delivering Universal UCC™ with Amadeo™. The technology in the Amadeo UCC solution will connect and interoperate with all existing major UC/UCC solutions such as Microsoft® Lync®, Google™ Hangouts™, Cisco® Jabber®/WebEx®, and IBM® Sametime®. Damaka&apos;s patented \"managed peer-to-peer SIP\" based software solutions feature SmartShare™/TabShare™, Parallel Edits™, Federated services across Amadeo on-prem and cloud deployments, and Sweeping®, which allows users to seamlessly transfer in-progress collaboration sessions to and from various devices including laptops, tablets and smartphones. The Damaka Universal UCC offering provides a unique solution for service providers, enterprises, and small & medium sized businesses to meet their specific needs with respect to telephony, Video, Collaboration and Mobility. Damaka was founded in 2004 and is headquartered in Richardson, Texas, USA. Latest Tweet Damaka Introduces Amadeo Cloud™ #UCC Service for Small to Medium Sized Businesses http://t.co/i13jImxJCx #SMB #mobilebiz #VoIP #enterprise3:42 PM Jul 31st Contact Us 2460 N. Central Expressway, Richardson, TX 75080, USA +1 (972) 696 0080 info@amadeocloud.com Follow Us Twitter LinkedIn © 2014 Damaka, Inc. All Rights Reserved. Privacy Policy Terms of Use ',' language english espa','About Amadeo Cloud: The Company','ok',38,38,'',15258,'https://amadeocloud.com/acerca.php','d7db72fe193b38b7a9fa52437c5f801e',-1,0,''),(40,'https://amadeocloud.com/agentsprogram.php','',' Language: English Español | User Log In | Admin Log In | Register Toggle navigation Amadeo Cloud Product About Amadeo Features Compare Versions Voice Services SIP Trunks Amadeo Numbers Pricing Amadeo UCC Licensing Voice Services Support FAQ Client Download Partners Partner With Us Amadeo Reseller Program Amadeo Agent Program Company About Us Contact Partners Home Partners Amadeo Agent Program Amadeo Agent Program The Amadeo Agent Program (AAP) is designed to work as a referral program. It allows business pr